PrecisAppointment of Arthur William Sterritt, of Prince Rupert, British Columbia, as a British Columbia Treaty Commissioner, to hold office during pleasure commencing on the date of the present Order in Council, or the date of the Order issued by the Provincial Government, or the date of the Resolution of the First Nations Summit and ending April 14, 1995 or the date on which the appointemnt is revoked by resolution of the Summit.
